，所以每次轉倉都會比有底水補償番利息差，成交量大方便資金隨時調動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加息咪會跌價<br />\n咁咪會蝕？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，但係相對息會收多左。"},{"pid":"e0ed6326784758fa61eb4b10fbf6a43d149dc27f","tid":50500,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買到，利息要抽稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以會用第二個方法代為持有美債，就係用債券期貨。簡單d講一張合約等於一張美債，3個月轉一次倉，因為期貨冇息派嘅關係，所以每次轉倉都會比有底水補償番利息差，成交量大方便資金隨時調動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加息咪會跌價<br />\n咁咪會蝕？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，但係相對息會收多左。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但債券期貨無息喎"},{"pid":"df35b6a50851c618c39997d87d27b27cc7e2de21","tid":50500,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加息咪會跌價<br />\n咁咪會蝕？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，但係相對息會收多左。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但債券期貨無息喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉倉會有底水，補番息個部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee045e0c1329791b3794405d473e68000205bf40","tid":50500,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，但係相對息會收多左。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但債券期貨無息喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉倉會有底水，補番息個部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係幾明底水<br />\n咩原理？"},{"pid":"8c3694923a88a3d93e4d92a39d5285444f15963e","tid":50500,"uid":59586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"因為你期貨冇息收 期貨個價會扣左利息個價值"},{"pid":"a7ca7bb2e02589ba7ffbca6c8d4ebf127902100d","tid":50500,"uid":54833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"2%好多定期都有，見有D銀行！"},{"pid":"3588b652512c822bc6f3e947d12b7dce6bdefc44","tid":50500,"uid":5067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"買2800好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7febe2da2d2bd94a754631a674bfcc7d2c042b70","tid":50500,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"順手一問，宜家買大中華公司債基金點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8f7250caf61839969eb924d111ee999005bfa6","tid":50500,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你期貨冇息收 期貨個價會扣左利息個價值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以理解為期指同恆指嘅關係<br />\n<br />\n期指類比為債券期貨<br />\n恆指=一個會派息嘅股票組合，類比為會派息嘅債券<br />\n<br />\n債券期貨同現貨關係<br />\n<br />\ncash price = (futures price * conversion factor) + basis"},{"pid":"5b205faa98662785b914b13a0f5a99d470ece785","tid":50500,"uid":54913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2%好多定期都有，見有D銀行！</blockquote><br />\n例如？<br />\n我搵到最多1.95% 做三個月炸"},{"pid":"c6aec6ce3c3a825e6b7a6620f1509cf77e31d079","tid":50500,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"我見獅子銀行有得買美債 手續費都好平 有冇人試過？"},{"pid":"8bb5f9e755c98f319e8868fecf7d08f05475b9cd","tid":50500,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見獅子銀行有得買美債 手續費都好平 有冇人試過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美債就算10年期嘅都有好多種，因為佢係不停出，每隻到期日都唔同，有d可能仲有幾年到期，有d就可能岩岩出，所以你會見到個價會唔一樣，比股票複雜好多。<br />\n<br />\n而且同股票唔同，債券係行莊家制，係睇個莊開咩價。"},{"pid":"7532b897297a461c7cc07e2cbd3cfef3419dd3d4","tid":50500,"uid":8133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見獅子銀行有得買美債 手續費都好平 有冇人試過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美債半年出一次，唔同到期日價同息率都唔同，美債因為普及同流通量高，所以一般mark up 較少，主要留意存倉費，有興趣要周圍格價好啲"},{"pid":"03d84436b13bca247db368d43b88d7449b91ef63","tid":50500,"uid":54913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"認購新債券  揸到到期 係冇蝕 仲有息賺"},{"pid":"514ca46c89696773dde9e7da075b3808f49bdf9d","tid":50500,"uid":54913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認購新債券  揸到到期 係冇蝕 仲有息賺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認購新債券  揸到到期 唔計滙率 係咪包冇蝕 仲有息賺？"}]}